      • AttributeManager

        public AttributeManager(SkillAPI api)
        Sets up the attribute manager, loading the attribute data from the configuration. This is handled by SkillAPI automatically so other plugins should not instantiate this class.
        Parameters:
        api - SkillAPI reference
